title: NY Tri Expo 2016- Registrants
desc: If you ever thought about doing a triathlon or if you are an experienced triathlete, then you won't want to miss the NY TRI EXPO '16, scheduled for Saturday, March 19 at 10 am - 6 pm at Citi Field in NYC! There will be three learning tracks from "Should I be a triathlete?" and "How to breath under water" to "After Ironman what happens next?" to "Should I get a power meter?" Admission fee includes: Purchase your tickets today!? At the door, tickets will be sold for $65.00 each.? Have a question? Contact us at nytriexpo@gmail.com or visit  NYTriExpo.com !
